# Optional: override WebSocket URL (CrazyGames, staging, custom backend).
#
# If unset:
#   - npm run dev (Vite) → same-origin /ws (proxy to local game server)
#   - production build (vite build, static preview, third-party hosts) →
#     wss://orbeats.fly.dev/ws
#
# Example overrides:
# VITE_WS_URL=wss://ws.orbeats.online/ws
# VITE_WS_URL=wss://staging.example.com/ws
